data.meta_description: Actor. He is best remembered for his role of the Cisco Kid in the early talking movie In Old Arizona (1929), which won him an Oscar for Best Actor that same year. It was his only Oscar. He reprised the role twice, for the films The Cisco Kid (1931) and The Return of the Cisco Kid (1939). Born Warner Leroy Baxter in...
